          "BTTInlineAppleScript" : "property storedInputLevel : missing value\r\rif input volume of (get volume settings) is 0 then\r\t-- we're muted, so it's time to unmute\r\tif storedInputLevel is missing value then\r\t\tset storedInputLevel to 75\r\tend if\r\t\r\t-- get the saved input level, and restore it\r\tset volume input volume storedInputLevel\r\t\relse\r\t-- we're unmuted, so it's time to mute\r\t\r\ttell application \"System Events\"\r\t\t-- save the current input volume setting --\r\t\tset storedInputLevel to input volume of (get volume settings)\r\tend tell\r\t\r\t-- mute the input\r\tset volume input volume 0\r\t\rend if\r\rreturn input volume of (get volume settings)",
